@startuml login_jwt_flow
skinparam backgroundColor #1a1a2e
skinparam defaultFontColor #e0e0e0
skinparam defaultFontName "DejaVu Sans"
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

skinparam participant {
  BackgroundColor #16213e
  BorderColor #6200EE
  FontColor #ffffff
  BorderThickness 2
}
skinparam actor {
  BackgroundColor #16213e
  BorderColor #03DAC6
  FontColor #03DAC6
}
skinparam arrow {
  Color #03DAC6
  FontColor #e0e0e0
  FontSize 12
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #0f3460
  BorderColor #6200EE
  FontColor #ddd
}
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #6200EE

title <color:#ffffff><size:20>Login & JWT Token Flow</size></color>

actor User
participant "LoginScreen\n(Jetpack Compose)" as UI #0f3460
participant "AuthViewModel" as VM #0f3460
participant "AuthRepository" as AuthRepo #16213e
participant "Firebase Auth\nSDK (local)" as SDK #8B0000
participant "Firebase Auth\nServer" as FBServer #8B0000
participant "Firestore DB" as FS #00008B

User -> UI: Enter Email, Password\nTap "Login"
activate UI

UI -> VM: login(email, psw)
activate VM
VM -> VM: authState = Loading

VM -> AuthRepo: login(email, psw)
activate AuthRepo

AuthRepo -> SDK: signInWithEmailAndPassword(email, psw)
activate SDK

SDK -> FBServer: HTTPS POST /identitytoolkit\n{ email, password }
activate FBServer

note over FBServer
  Server verifies password hash
  against stored credential
end note

FBServer --> SDK: ID Token (JWT)\n+ Refresh Token
deactivate FBServer

note over SDK
  JWT Payload contains:
  { "uid": "abc123",
    "email": "user@x.ca",
    "exp": 1713680000 }
  Signed with Firebase private key
end note

SDK -> SDK: Cache JWT locally\n(expires in 1 hour)
SDK --> AuthRepo: FirebaseUser(uid)
deactivate SDK

AuthRepo --> VM: FirebaseUser
deactivate AuthRepo

VM -> VM: authState = Success
VM --> UI: authState = Success
deactivate VM

UI --> User: Navigate to Art List
deactivate UI

== Later: Firestore Request ==

UI -> FS: getArtworks() / getUserProfile()
activate FS

note over FS
  Firebase SDK automatically attaches:
  Authorization: Bearer <JWT>
  to every Firestore gRPC request
end note

FS -> FS: Verify JWT signature\nCheck request.auth.uid\nagainst Security Rules
FS --> UI: Authorized data response
deactivate FS

== After 1 hour: Auto Token Refresh ==

SDK -> FBServer: POST /token\n{ refreshToken }
activate FBServer
FBServer --> SDK: New ID Token (JWT)
deactivate FBServer
note over SDK: App continues seamlessly\nwithout user re-login

@enduml
